text: @FedEx I will no longer do business with you while you cheerfully partner with the NRA to support the slaughter of innocents while you line your pockets and theirs with blood money.
@FedExHelp This is not the level of service I’ve come to expect from FedEx. If you’d like all the tracking info, I’ll be happy to PM it. Check out this trashed box! https://t.co/0jvSWgeL7A
@kathybiallas Hi Kathryn, this is Kelly. I do apologize for any frustration or inconvenience. Can you please confirm if your shipment contents were intact?
@FedExHelp Some of the contents (multiple small items) had the boxes squished as well. It doesn’t matter what they contained; this should not be the state of any delivered package.

@kathybiallas Hello Kathryn, this is Rochelle. Kelly has stepped out of the office. Packages go through rigorous processes designed to optimize efficient and fast shipping. This process includes employees manually unloading conveyables onto a conveyor belt.

@kathybiallas While our drivers strive to handle each shipment in a professional and business-like manner, the exterior of packages can sometimes receive minor damage on the conveyor belts and during the transiting process. I am glad your contents did not withstand any loss or damage.
Rochelle
